{"tid":2095783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男友：你同林鄭有咩分別？","createTime":"2020-07-05T17:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T11:57:05.000Z","uid":322645,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"103cf565d3f3b611b3573659e39d86dbd87908de","tid":2095783,"uid":322645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T17:43:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">話說我呢兩個月織緊嘢<br />\n可能因為無乜天份<br />\n所以成日織錯<br />\n錯咗就要拆咗重新嚟過<br />\n今日全日都陷入咗個織完又拆<br />\n拆完又織嘅淪迥<br />\n<br />\n於是我崩潰咗<br />\n我就喊住打俾我男朋友<br />\n佢就答我以下嘅說話：<br />\n<br />\n「咁不嬲織嘢都係咁。<br />\n咁你想織到完全冇錯嘅話，<br />\n就要喺錯嘅地方返轉頭重新嚟過，<br />\n咁好正常嘅。<br />\n唔係淨係你先要經歷呢啲情況㗎係咪先？<br />\n咁你又唔使咁誇張要喊，<br />\n又要話唔織又要話想燒咗佢。<br />\n咁係咪所有嘢處理唔到嘅時候就要令嗰樣嘢消失先？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁你同林鄭有咩分別？</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">真人真事 有錄音檔喺手<br />\n有無男朋友可以衰得過我呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我聽完喊得仲勁咗</span>"},{"pid":"ba0d38387b7d791b4c6d456b90cc962da0bfa277","tid":2095783,"uid":218575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T17:44:06.000Z","msg":"同我一齊"},{"pid":"cdd7b354db6f59f522537f2e18da00af34e6587d","tid":2095783,"uid":61416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T17:44:48.000Z","msg":"感情問題"},{"pid":"6f10c34e89bb7c222da70b19885160e39b709998","tid":2095783,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T17:46:01.000Z","msg":"樓豬係淋病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c678c9fc4753c6be847fbc4a65a769e2ec0c93d","tid":2095783,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"求錄音檔"},{"pid":"060fb3b194d75cd323bf517c06448b129f9c50ef","tid":2095783,"uid":303728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"103cf565d3f3b611b3573659e39d86dbd87908de","tid":2095783,"uid":322645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T17:43:40.000Z","msg":"<span st